<p>
<lb n="1"/>nirantaṉūr cokkapperumāḷukkup pottappiyil
<lb n="2"/>tiruviṭaiyāṭṭa nilamutal ceṟkkum paṭṭiyil kālvā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yppaṟṟil patine<unclear>ḻa</unclear>ṭikkol nilaṅkuḻi Āyirattaññūṟu
<lb n="4"/>periyaerikiḻ cuṇṭilpaṟṟil nilaṅkuḻi Eḻuṉūṟṟaimpatu
<lb n="5"/>paṇṭiyaṟvāyil nilaṅkuḻi <unclear>Eḻu</unclear>ṉūṟṟaimpatu citteppo
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tteṉpaṭṭiyil kuḻi Āyirattampatu cammippaṭṭi ku
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḻi Āyiram <g type="ddanda">.</g>
<lb n="8"/>maṟikkuṇṭai nilaṅkuḻi Āyiram <g type="ddanda">.</g>
<lb n="9"/>cintalppāḻ nilaṅ kuḻi Āyiram <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

